<p><ent>Lunge</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Lunge
<hw>Lunge</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cause to go round in a ring, as
a horse, while holding his halter.</def>
<rj><au>Thackeray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lunge</ent>⟦br⟧

